            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p class="type-body text-warm-mid pb-2">Completely. Clean, documented code that's yours. Hand it to any developer. Move it anywhere. No&nbsp;lock-in.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
